Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.89,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.39,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:27.77,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
