Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:44.45,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.58,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:56.47,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.64,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.43,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.56,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.02,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.11,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
